      </div>
      
      <div class="topic-item card-dark">
        <div class="topic-icon">ðŸŽ¨</div>
        <h3 class="heading-md">Design Tips</h3>
        <p class="body-text">Get insights on creating designs that work well for embroidery and printing, including color choices and sizing.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="topic-item card-dark">
        <div class="topic-icon">ðŸ’¡</div>
        <h3 class="heading-md">Industry Insights</h3>
        <p class="body-text">Stay updated on industry trends, new technologies, and changes in the custom apparel market.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="topic-item card-dark">
